yingyinNormal.en: You got a problem. Just one?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有个麻烦。才一个吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And now? Now there's only one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在呢？只剩一个了。

yingyinNormal.en: First to ride one, though. So?
yingyinNormal.zh: 也是第一个骑龙的维京人，为什么?

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, which one is Bonnie again?
yingyinNormal.zh: 邦妮是哪一个？

yingyinNormal.en: Now we can go to the other one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在我们可以转向另一个。

yingyinNormal.en: There is one. Precinct 47. Here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有一个，在第四十七区域，这里。

yingyinNormal.en: Aw, damn it. Hand me another one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我靠，再给我递一个。

yingyinNormal.en: There's one of those ancients now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 眼前就出现了一个古人。

yingyinNormal.en: They're only taking one this year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今年他们只录取一个。

yingyinNormal.en: They make it? Neither one of them?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们都没活下来? 一个也没有?

yingyinNormal.en: How many people you kill? Only one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 杀了多少人? 只有一个

yingyinNormal.en: Because God know you gonna need one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为很明显你现在需要这么一个。

yingyinNormal.en: There's one last surprise. Follow me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有最后一个惊喜哦，跟我来！

yingyinNormal.en: Can now be accomplished by one person.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在只要一个人就可以完成。

yingyinNormal.en: One orc could not kill a world, Durotan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 单凭一个兽人是无法毁灭世界的，杜隆坦。

yingyinNormal.en: I knew it. I knew l wasn't the only one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就知道不可能只有我一个!

yingyinNormal.en: Of course they are. Leonard's being one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然有，莱纳德就是一个。

yingyinNormal.en: I am in the mix. And I'm the hottest one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我跻身经典集锦中了，而且我是最漂亮的一个。

yingyinNormal.en: Structure, constant structure. One atom...
yingyinNormal.zh: 结构，恒定结构，一个原子……

yingyinNormal.en: This is one way. Plan B, a population bomb.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一个办法B计划，超级人口炸弹。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>One</highlight> afternoon, while attempting to get into bed she collapsed (倒下) from what was eventually discovered to be a heart attack.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一天下午，当她试图上床睡觉时，突然倒下，最终被发现是心脏病发作。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>One</highlight> reason is that most people are not even aware of their mispronunciations.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 原因之一是，大多数人甚至没有意识到自己的发音错误。

examination_example.sentence: It only has <highlight>one</highlight> bedroom, but it sounds nice, near Lake Street.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它只有一个卧室，但听起来不错，靠近湖街。

examination_example.sentence: I quickly graduated from typical children's books to <highlight>ones</highlight> with fewer pictures and longer chapters.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我很快从典型的儿童读物升级到图片更少、章节更长的读物。

examination_example.sentence: I have searched through dozens of plays to find the <highlight>ones</highlight> that I think best show the  purpose of the short play.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我搜索了几十个剧本，寻找我认为最能展示这个短剧的目的的剧本。

examination_example.sentence: They require a bigger commitment than smaller <highlight>ones</highlight>, and they have a more powerful effect on the feeling of a space.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们需要比较小的承诺更大的承诺，并且他们对空间的感觉有更强的影响。

examination_example.sentence: The study also suggests that the right level of background noise may actually improve <highlight>one</highlight>'s creative thinking ability.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究还表明，适当的背景噪音实际上可以提高一个人的创造性思维能力。

examination_example.sentence: Humor can improve <highlight>one</highlight>'s  appearance/look and personality.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 幽默可以改善一个人的外表/样子和性格。

word_usage.usage: one用于形容词之后：Your plan is a good one on paper. 你的计划在理论上是个好计划。

sense_info_list.zh: 一; 一个(人); 唯一

examination_example.sentence: Children from <highlight>one</highlight>-child families need strict rules.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 独生子女家庭的孩子需要严格的管理。

examination_example.sentence: It is <highlight>one</highlight> of the most popular English songs of all time．
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是有史以来最受欢迎的英文歌之一。

examination_example.sentence: It was the most difficult <highlight>one</highlight> of all.
Now no <highlight>one</highlight> could eat the apples, and the apple tree died !
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在没人能吃苹果了，苹果树死了！

examination_example.sentence: No <highlight>one</highlight> wakes up feeling happy every day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没有人每天醒来都觉得快乐。

examination_example.sentence: My grandma's story has shown me what it takes to realize <highlight>one</highlight>'s dream.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我奶奶的故事告诉了我怎样才能实现一个人的梦想。

sense_info_list.en: referring  a person or a thing previously mentioned

examination_example.sentence: But as time goes by, some new dreams have appeared and some old <highlight>ones</highlight> have disappeared.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但随着时间的推移，一些新的梦想出现了，一些旧的梦想消失了。

examination_example.sentence: This street is much wider than that <highlight>one</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这条街比那条街宽得多。

examination_example.sentence: Tony's job is very different from any other job I've heard of, but it is a really important <highlight>one</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 托尼的工作和我听说过的其他工作很不一样，但这确实是一份非常重要的工作。

examination_example.sentence: Can you imagine how happy your beloved <highlight>one</highlight> will be happy when you give him/her your?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你能想象当你把你的爱给他/她时，他/她会有多开心吗？

examination_example.sentence: She said that you're the only <highlight>one</highlight> failing in her class.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她说你是她班上唯一一个不及格的。

word_usage.usage:
one作名词时可数，复数为ones。
There's one bad apple for every three good ones.
每四个苹果里就有一个坏的。
